channel.title: Client for my server
channel.description:
I am using a Delta server. (Dont judge me, Ive always liked delta)
Anyways my dad reset our computer and now my client doesnt work right it bugs up and glitches alot.. I was wondering where is a very basic client that works with delta that i can download? I would like something very very basic, as i am using dialup at this house. I usually download stuff at a different location, but i cannot get to that computer to download my things.
[b]I DONT WANT TO HEAR ANYONE DISSING ME BECAUSE I GOT DIALUP AT HOME, THAT WOULD SHOW WHAT A NO LIFE YOU REALLY ARE.[/b]
JUST ANSWER MY QUESTION, IF YOU CANNOT ANSWER MY QUESTION PLEASE MOVE ON [color=white][size=8pt]Comments about my dialup or that are just dissing me will be gladly deleted =)[/size]
